trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of toolbar to display.
trans-unit.target: Angir hvilken type verktøylinjen for å vise.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by members such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolBar.Appearance%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Denne nummerering brukes av medlemmer som <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolBar.Appearance%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolBar.Appearance%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Set the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolBar.Appearance%2A> property of the toolbar to `ToolBarAppearance.Flat` to give the toolbar and its buttons a flat appearance.
trans-unit.target: Angi den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolBar.Appearance%2A>for verktøylinjen for å `ToolBarAppearance.Flat` slik at verktøylinjen og tilhørende knapper en flat virkning.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.ToolBar.Appearance%2A>

trans-unit.source: As the mouse pointer moves over the buttons, their appearance changes to three-dimensional.
trans-unit.target: Som musen flytter pekeren over knappene endringer utseendet til tredimensjonale.

trans-unit.source: Button separators appear as lines rather than spaces between the buttons when the toolbar has a flat appearance.
trans-unit.target: Knappen skilletegn vises som linjer i stedet for mellomrom mellom knappene når verktøylinjen har et flatt utseende.

trans-unit.source: The toolbar and buttons appear flat, but the buttons change to three-dimensional as the mouse pointer moves over them.
trans-unit.target: Verktøylinjen og knapper vises flate, men knappene endre til tredimensjonale som flytter pekeren over dem.

trans-unit.source: The toolbar and buttons appear as standard three-dimensional controls.
trans-unit.target: Vises som standard tredimensjonale Kontroller verktøylinjen og knapper.
